 The Weight of Rain 

 
 
 

 
 



 
 

 
 



 





 
 
 
 
 

 
 

 
 

 

 By  Jonathan Corum 
 Feb. 8, 2014 

 Update: a video of my talk is posted above. 

 Below is a summary of my talk at the second  Visualized  conference, which was held yesterday at the Times Center. 

 I’m writing from memory so this is only an approximation of what I said. 

 

 Photo by  Gregor Aisch 

 Photo by  Gregor Aisch 

 

 

 
 Good morning! 
 My name is Jonathan Corum and I work upstairs. 
 

 

 HMWhite 

 
 Cube 
 I know many of you were at the  Dome    last night, but I wanted to start this morning with a Cube. 
 Behind me, behind this screen, is a 70-foot cube planted with birch trees. 
 

 

